{"tid":55544,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"樂視再傳「拖數」 英超中國區直播今晚或被終止","createTime":"2016-12-26T13:16:15.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-26T14:43:11.000Z","uid":48083,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c18e8805ecd327402434e6bd76392e3265e71b23","tid":55544,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T13:16:15.000Z","msg":"樂視爆煲事件繼續發酵，繼傳出聖誕節前夕「大刀闊斧」裁員60人後，內地網媒《36氪》引述消息報道，指樂視拖欠英超中國版權商新英體育3000萬美元的費用，故後者或按照合約，在英超第18輪（即今晚）切斷向樂視提供的直播信號。 <br />\n<br />\n消息指，樂視體育於今年8月與新英體育合作，獲得了英超的轉播權，而據悉樂視需向新英體育分兩期支付費用，第一期已支付，惟應於上周支付的第二期，即 3000萬美元，則仍未支付。<br />\n<br />\n本報已向樂視查詢，惟暫未獲得回覆。<br />\n<br />\n- See more at: <a href=\"http://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1482745139597&amp;issue=20161226#sthash.occ66S2e.dpuf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1482745139597%26issue%3D20161226%23sthash.occ66S2e.dpuf&d=DcIovIHe8v2fPO%2BdLmikTwT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=f5d4b311\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1482745139597%26issue%3D20161226%23sthash.occ66S2e.dpuf&h=c46100dd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1482745139597&amp;issue=20161226#sthash.occ66S2e.dpuf</a>"},{"pid":"4aa8c9bb86e0d2ac800478a308eb8003c7fe8ef5","tid":55544,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T13:17:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 終於收皮"},{"pid":"fb1b559897d5c9bfecad20ce03a64c72847ce179","tid":55544,"uid":12021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T13:17:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b4ec973c1e9827975d0ac8d2c9078ab17649e50e","tid":55544,"uid":55077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T13:19:54.000Z","msg":"食住在chips睇樂視收皮<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SAT2R.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSAT2R.gif&h=9219877b&s={S